==General guidelines==

The primary frequency range of the cello is 56-520 Hz with overtones up to 8kHz

===Microphone placement===
'''Each technique begins with a bullet point'''

*Place a microphone (with a flat frequency response) level and directed toward the sound hole between 6 inches to 3 feet away.




